.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, reggae, ambient, folk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, weightlifting, volleyball, rugby
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
2. the fan of folk is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
3. the fan of folk is on the far right##1
4. the fan of reggae is the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the fan of ambient is between the fan of funk and the fan of reggae##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | reggae     | ambient           | funk | folk  |
| Sport         | handball | rugby | weightlifting   | volleyball |

