.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, soul, folk, hip-hop
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, bike, tram, helicopter
1. the fan of soul is the person driving the trike##1
2. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the fan of classical##1
4. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the fan of classical is between the person driving the trike and the fan of folk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | soul | classical | folk      |
| Transport     | tram | trike    | bike  | helicopter |

