.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, snowboarding, water-polo, sailing
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, bike, bus, skateboard
1. the person driving the subway is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person driving the bike is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person driving the bus##2
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | baseball | sailing | water-polo     | snowboarding   |
| Transport   | bus   | bike     | skateboard | subway |

