.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, peas, asparagus, raspberry
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, rowing, surfing, cycling
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
3. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating peas##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
5. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person eating peas and the person who's sport is cycling##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food    | raspberry   | asparagus      | peas   | carrot  |
| Sport   | cycling | rowing | surfing | parkour |

