.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, lettuce, banana, papaya
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, family, satire, disaster
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
2. the person eating lettuce is between the person eating papaya and the person eating pineapple##2
3. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
4. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Food          | pineapple     | lettuce | papaya   | banana        |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | satire   | family | disaster |

