.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, baking, sudoku, collecting
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, techno, metal, rock
1. the fan of metal is the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the fan of techno is on the left of the fan of rock##1
3. the fan of blues is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the fan of techno##1
5. the fan of blues is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
6. the fan of techno is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person who's hobby is collecting##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | baking | sudoku | collecting | board-games |
| Music-Genre   | metal          | techno     | rock  | blues     |

