2. the accountant is between the person watching spy movies and the videographer##2
3. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
4. the videographer is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | videographer | accountant | coach | bartender     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | romance    | spy   | horror |

