.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, german, turkish, chinese
4 different pets are kept: dog, fish, hamster, ferret
1. the malaysian is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the chinese is the owner of the hamster##1
3. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the dog and the german##2
4. the owner of the ferret is the owner of the ferret##1
5. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | chinese | german | malaysian | turkish |
| Pet           | hamster  | ferret  | fish | dog      |

