.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, italian, nigerian, pakistani
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, badminton, biathlon, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the pakistani is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the spanish and the nigerian##2
5. the nigerian is the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | pakistani   | spanish   | italian | nigerian |
| Sport         | snowboarding | badminton | water-polo     | biathlon    |

