.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, puzzles, rock-climbing, filmmaking
4 different pets are kept: snake, horse, dog, rat
1. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is between the owner of the snake and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing    | filmmaking     | camping | puzzles |
| Pet     | horse | rat | dog       | snake     |

 